data.description: MUST SEE!!!! Beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bath brick 1 Story with full finished basement & loads up updates! Move into this gorgeous home today! The kitchen features cherry raised panel cabinets with hardware, granite counters, accenting glass tile back splash, fixtures, and all stainless steel appliance package! Modern dark stained hardwood floors in the large living room & main level bedrooms! Both full bathrooms have modern vanities & custom tiled showers! Move in & enjoy the full finished basement which includes a huge family room, spacious laundry & storage area, additional bed & bathroom! Fenced in yard with a gate along the side driveway to the 2-car garage. Fenced-in yard with a gate along the side driveway to the detached 2-car garage. Property is close to transportation, highway, and nearby shopping.
